thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Warren Moore

author: Warren Moore
title: Warren Moore
text: I have rented cars from Omega now many times and would not go past them for service, price, car quality, reliability and just plainly great guys to deal with. It would be that I am unable to have them as a first choice option that I would use someone else. Highly recommended.
